  description: "socket.SocketKind enum member integer value checks in socketeq217a namespace — wave 217 theme: SOCK_STREAM.value == 1; SOCK_DGRAM.value == 2; SOCK_RAW.value == 3; these values correspond to the POSIX SOCK_* constants and are stable across all POSIX platforms; the .value attribute of an IntEnum returns the underlying integer; verified with Python 3.14.3"
